Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.16,0:00:10.51,Tonari-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.51,0:00:11.69,Tonari-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like a Baby Star monja and a
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.69,0:00:13.71,Tonari-main,,0000,0000,0000,,cod roe mochi cheese and seafood monja!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.71,0:00:15.20,Tonari-main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,Wow...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.20,0:00:16.35,Tonari-main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,You're still hungry?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.38,0:00:18.32,Tonari-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.32,0:00:20.08,Tonari-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,I need to eat my mind out!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.06,0:00:25.49,Tonari-internal/narrator,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,My heart's still pounding...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.07,0:00:27.98,Tonari-internal/narrator,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,Probably because I was so surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.83,0:00:30.28,Tonari-internal/narrator,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,That must be it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.91,0:00:35.01,Tonari-main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,I've never had anything \Nthis good before.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.59,0:00:40.43,Tonari-main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,I guess everything tastes \Ngood when I'm with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.91,0:00:44.89,Tonari-internal/narrator,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,The strange throbbing in my chest \Nshows no sign of slowing.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.89,0:00:48.52,Tonari-internal/narrator,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,I more or less know \Nwhat's causing it...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.14,0:00:51.43,Tonari-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,A mixed monja with a \Ndouble helping of pork!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.43,0:00:53.24,Tonari-main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?  You're still not done?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.35,0:00:57.60,Tonari-internal/narrator,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,In any case,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.60,0:01:00.52,Tonari-internal/narrator,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,I enjoyed my first experience \Nwith monjayaki,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.52,0:01:02.13,Tonari-internal/narrator,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,so it wasn't all bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.00,0:02:38.01,Tonari-ep-title-black-big,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,Weird
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.36,0:02:44.37,Tonari-internal/narrator,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,From a young age, my only \Nconcern was my grades.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.97,0:02:48.02,Tonari-internal/narrator,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't care about anybody \Nelse or anything else.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.28,0:02:52.30,Tonari-internal/narrator,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,My world began and ended with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.01,0:02:56.57,Tonari-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,1,300 yen for a box of potatoes...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.08,0:02:58.95,Tonari-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,To achieve a 30% margin,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.95,0:03:00.70,Tonari-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,each 700 gram bag
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.12,0:03:02.54,Tonari-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,should be priced at 138 yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.87,0:03:05.70,Tonari-main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.70,0:03:07.25,Tonari-main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.25,0:03:08.34,Tonari-main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Something on your mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.34,0:03:09.72,Tonari-main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,That's rare.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.60,0:03:13.35,Tonari-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,If my father knew how to \Ncalculate unit prices,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.35,0:03:15.34,Tonari-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't have to waste my time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.91,0:03:16.88,Tonari-main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Keep it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.88,0:03:20.63,cuumbers,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,Cucumbers 100 yen each
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.82,0:03:20.63,Tonari-internal/narrator,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,Something's wrong with me these days.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.63,0:03:25.59,cuumbers,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Half Price
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.26,0:03:23.89,Tonari-internal/narrator,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm unable to concentrate \Non anything I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.53,0:03:25.60,Tonari-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,Samejima-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.29,0:03:28.92,Tonari-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,Could you stop putting new \Nhalf-price stickers on these?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.01,0:03:35.93,Tonari-internal/narrator,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,I certainly understand why that is...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.54,0:03:42.49,Tonari-main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,Make-up exam?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.06,0:03:44.56,Tonari-main,Sae,0000,0000,0000,,Every student who failed a midterm
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.56,0:03:46.50,Tonari-main,,0000,0000,0000,,is required to take the make-up!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.04,0:03:48.67,Tonari-main,Sae,0000,0000,0000,,Since you forgot to put your name
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.67,0:03:50.09,Tonari-main,,0000,0000,0000,,and received a zero in every subject,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.09,0:03:51.35,Tonari-main,Sae,0000,0000,0000,,you have to take make-ups!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.35,0:03:53.13,Tonari-main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,Are you taking make-ups?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.13,0:03:54.22,Tonari-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,As if.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.22,0:03:56.28,Tonari-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,I had the highest score in our grade.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.89,0:03:59.48,Tonari-main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,Then I won't take them either.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.37,0:04:01.09,Tonari-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.79,0:04:04.14,Tonari-internal/narrator,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,He would have
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.14,0:04:06.78,Tonari-internal/narrator,,0000,0000,0000,,scored higher than me \Nif he had put his name...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.15,0:04:26.38,Tonari-main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,B-But, I saw him walking around \Nin the rain on my way to school!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.38,0:04:28.04,Tonari-main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you feel bad for him?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.04,0:04:28.62,Tonari-main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.04,0:04:30.97,Tonari-main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,Tsk.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.83,0:04:37.08,box,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,Come see Yoshida in 1-B \Nif you want him as a pet.\N\NPick on him and I'll kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.26,0:04:35.40,Tonari-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.40,0:04:37.08,Tonari-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, this is Yoshida's?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.92,0:04:42.05,Tonari-internal/narrator,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,The students had gotten used to \NHaru's bizarre behavior by now,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.05,0:04:46.93,Tonari-internal/narrator,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,but there was a small\N revolution going on inside me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.06,0:04:52.75,Tonari-main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you ignoring me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.75,0:04:54.64,Tonari-main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,I've been trying to get your attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.68,0:04:57.28,Tonari-internal/narrator,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm painfully conscious \Nof his presence.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.86,0:04:59.91,Tonari-internal/narrator,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,Can you blame me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.52,0:05:04.06,Tonari-internal/narrator,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,I've never been close to \Nanother human before.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.06,0:05:06.19,Tonari-internal/narrator,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,How am I supposed to ignore him?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.04,0:05:13.48,Tonari-main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.48,0:05:15.19,Tonari-main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think you're doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.04,0:05:18.13,Tonari-main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,Don't pick on the rooster!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.35,0:05:22.23,Tonari-internal/narrator,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,He doesn't seem to care.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.23,0:05:23.80,Tonari-main,Natsu,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.80,0:05:25.25,Tonari-internal/narrator,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.25,0:05:26.62,Tonari-internal/narrator,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm acting like...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.75,0:05:26.62,Tonari-overlap,Natsu,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.62,0:05:28.15,Tonari-internal/narrator,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,...I'm in love with Haru.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.27,0:05:30.19,Tonari-main,Natsu,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.78,0:05:34.77,shoyo,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,Syoyo \NHigh \NSchool
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.52,0:05:34.07,Tonari-internal/narrator,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,This could be difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.41,0:05:38.30,Tonari-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,Haru.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.30,0:05:39.10,Tonari-main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.10,0:05:42.16,Tonari-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,You said that y—
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.85,0:05:44.53,Tonari-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,You love me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.88,0:05:47.18,Tonari-main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,Yep.  I love you, Shizuku.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.49,0:05:50.28,Tonari-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,In a romantic way?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.28,0:05:52.28,Tonari-main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,I would totally do you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.66,0:05:54.29,Tonari-internal/narrator,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,What's that supposed to mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.41,0:05:58.82,Tonari-main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, can you take the rooster?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.82,0:06:00.73,Tonari-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't mind me deep frying him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.73,0:06:01.74,Tonari-main,Natsu,0000,0000,0000,,Mi—
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.74,0:06:03.21,Tonari-main,Natsu,0000,0000,0000,,Mizutani-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.19,0:06:09.18,cleaners,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,Cleaners
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.05,0:06:16.81,Tonari-main,Natsu,0000,0000,0000,,Please help me study!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.81,0:06:19.06,tecchan,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,Tecchan\NOkonomiyaki\NMonja
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.25,0:06:22.06,Tonari-main,Natsu,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Natsume Asako.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.88,0:06:25.44,Tonari-main,Natsu,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know who I am?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.44,0:06:26.67,Tonari-main,Natsu,0000,0000,0000,,No?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.67,0:06:29.28,Tonari-main,Natsu,0000,0000,0000,,We're in the same class.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.81,0:06:34.44,Tonari-main,Natsu,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, Yoshida-kun \Nkeeps glaring at me...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.44,0:06:35.51,Tonari-main,Natsu,0000,0000,0000,,With that rooster...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.51,0:06:36.78,Tonari-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,Just ignore him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.78,0:06:38.62,Tonari-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,He's scared of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.49,0:06:40.58,Tonari-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.58,0:06:42.58,Tonari-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,Can I get another pork and \Negg with cod roe mochi?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.11,0:06:45.83,Tonari-main,Natsu,0000,0000,0000,,And I'd like the kimchi \Ntempura and curry mix.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.83,0:06:46.72,Tonari-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.72,0:06:48.97,Tonari-main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,You girls really like to eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.60,0:06:54.20,Tonari-main,Natsu,0000,0000,0000,,So, as I was saying before, \Nif I fail the make-up exams,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.20,0:06:56.41,Tonari-main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll have to take a \Nremedial class next week.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.93,0:06:58.49,Tonari-main,Natsu,0000,0000,0000,,However, I have an important
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.49,0:07:00.75,Tonari-main,,0000,0000,0000,,appointment with my friends that day,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.75,0:07:03.21,Tonari-main,Natsu,0000,0000,0000,,so I can't fail the exam.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.54,0:07:05.94,Tonari-main,Natsu,0000,0000,0000,,Mizutani-san, that's where—
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.94,0:07:07.45,Tonari-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,I refuse.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.85,0:07:11.49,Tonari-main,Natsu,0000,0000,0000,,I've done what I can,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.75,0:07:12.88,Tonari-main,Natsu,0000,0000,0000,,but...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.33,0:07:18.67,Tonari-main,Natsu,0000,0000,0000,,I'm too stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.60,0:07:20.83,Tonari-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,No kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.83,0:07:23.33,Tonari-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,You answered every question \Nand still failed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.36,0:07:27.09,Tonari-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, but that's your problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.51,0:07:31.05,Tonari-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,If you're so stupid, you should \Ntake the remedial class.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.05,0:07:32.68,Tonari-main,Natsu,0000,0000,0000,,Er, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.68,0:07:34.57,Tonari-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,There you go then.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.57,0:07:36.01,Tonari-main,Natsu,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.01,0:07:38.23,Tonari-main,Natsu,0000,0000,0000,,Please wait, Mizutani-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.01,0:07:43.02,tecchan,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,Tecchan\NOkonomiyaki\NMonja
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.23,0:07:39.58,Tonari-main,Natsu,0000,0000,0000,,I beg you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.21,0:07:43.02,Tonari-main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it stopped raining.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.42,0:07:46.73,Tonari-main,Natsu,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have time
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.73,0:07:48.76,Tonari-main,Natsu,0000,0000,0000,,to take a remedial class!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.10,0:07:58.51,Tonari-main,Natsu,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.51,0:08:00.36,Tonari-main,,0000,0000,0000,,I had too much to eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.42,0:08:03.47,Tonari-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,You were forcing yourself \Nto eat all of that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.47,0:08:06.50,Tonari-main,Natsu,0000,0000,0000,,If I were a light eater, \Ntoo many boys would fall for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.52,0:08:10.62,Tonari-main,Natsu,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure you've noticed how cute I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.62,0:08:12.96,Tonari-main,Natsu,0000,0000,0000,,Boys always flock to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.96,0:08:16.22,Tonari-main,Natsu,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I'm always shunned by girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.64,0:08:18.93,Tonari-main,Natsu,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wait for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.25,0:08:24.03,Tonari-main,Natsu,0000,0000,0000,,That spot is dry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.97,0:08:26.97,Tonari-main,Natsu,0000,0000,0000,,Please look at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.42,0:08:35.91,hscommunity,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}High School Community
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.89,0:08:31.43,Tonari-main,Natsu,0000,0000,0000,,The appointment I mentioned earlier
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.43,0:08:33.36,Tonari-main,Natsu,0000,0000,0000,,was an offline gathering for the members
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.36,0:08:35.27,Tonari-main,,0000,0000,0000,,of an online community that I belong to.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.69,0:08:39.00,Tonari-main,Natsu,0000,0000,0000,,The members are all strangers,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.00,0:08:42.66,Tonari-main,Natsu,0000,0000,0000,,but they're the first \Nfriends I've ever made.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.78,0:08:47.31,Tonari-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,That's why you don't want \Nto take the remedial class?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.15,0:08:49.08,Tonari-main,Natsu,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.70,0:08:52.88,Tonari-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,I still refuse.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.88,0:08:54.72,Tonari-main,Natsu,0000,0000,0000,,Evil!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.72,0:08:56.86,Tonari-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,This is what you get \Nfor being a slacker.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.86,0:08:57.95,Tonari-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,Give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.95,0:08:59.35,Tonari-main,Natsu,0000,0000,0000,,Mercy, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.35,0:08:59.97,Tonari-main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.46,0:09:03.37,Tonari-main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,I can help you study.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.20,0:09:06.54,Tonari-main,Natsu,0000,0000,0000,,R-Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.54,0:09:08.31,Tonari-main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I got you covered.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.31,0:09:10.40,Tonari-main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,In return, take me with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.40,0:09:12.42,Tonari-main,Natsu,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!  Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.42,0:09:14.70,Tonari-main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,Will I be able to make friends \Nat this offline gathering?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.70,0:09:16.86,Tonari-main,Natsu,0000,0000,0000,,You bet!  You bet!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.08,0:09:20.22,Tonari-main,Natsu,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, but please don't \Nfall in love with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.22,0:09:21.17,Tonari-main,Natsu,0000,0000,0000,,It'd be a hassle.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.17,0:09:22.55,Tonari-main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, not a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.55,0:09:23.42,Tonari-main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,That's never happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.65,0:09:30.75,math,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,Math I
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.84,0:09:30.75,Tonari-main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,Let's start with math.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.98,0:09:32.84,Tonari-main,Natsu,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.84,0:09:33.96,Tonari-main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,Yep, you're welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.34,0:09:36.26,Tonari-internal/narrator,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,Why are they doing this here?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.26,0:09:37.81,Tonari-main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, watch closely.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.81,0:09:38.64,Tonari-main,Natsu,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.35,0:09:43.83,Tonari-main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,You do this...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.76,0:09:45.85,Tonari-main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,...to get this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.95,0:09:47.94,Tonari-main,Natsu,0000,0000,0000,,I don't understand!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.94,0:09:49.94,Tonari-main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, memorize that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.94,0:09:53.36,Tonari-main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,And for Japanese, English, \Nand history, read the textbook.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.36,0:09:54.18,Tonari-main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,All done.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.86,0:09:58.40,Tonari-internal/narrator,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,Well, at least I'm not \Nalone with Haru...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.40,0:09:59.42,Tonari-main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.09,0:10:03.40,Tonari-main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,You make the x squared an x.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.40,0:10:04.17,Tonari-main,Natsu,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.69,0:10:07.33,Tonari-main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,No, how did you get 5, stupid?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.98,0:10:08.74,Tonari-main,Natsu,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.74,0:10:10.55,Tonari-main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,Here, look closely.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.63,0:10:12.56,Tonari-main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,Not at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.56,0:10:13.58,Tonari-main,Natsu,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.58,0:10:14.81,Tonari-main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,You do this...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.92,0:10:19.19,Tonari-internal/narrator,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm?  What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.30,0:10:30.94,Tonari-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,You don't get any.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.81,0:10:34.76,Tonari-main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,Have you seen that girl around?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.76,0:10:36.32,Tonari-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You mean Natsume-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.53,0:10:38.51,Tonari-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.51,0:10:41.25,Tonari-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,Damn, where'd she go?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.83,0:10:45.14,Tonari-internal/narrator,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, there it is again.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.67,0:10:48.33,Tonari-internal/narrator,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,I feel so agitated.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.33,0:10:50.75,Tonari-main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,Nagoya, want some cabbage?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.65,0:10:55.75,Tonari-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,H-Ho—
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.75,0:10:57.55,Tonari-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,How's the studying going?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.43,0:11:02.06,Tonari-main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's too late to trade places now!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.06,0:11:03.38,Tonari-main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the one going to the offline event!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.38,0:11:04.26,Tonari-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,Not my point.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.70,0:11:08.69,Tonari-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,Is it really such a big deal?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.69,0:11:11.00,Tonari-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,You and Natsume-san are so odd.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.00,0:11:14.27,Tonari-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,Does it really matter that \Npeople don't like you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.80,0:11:18.99,Tonari-main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,You're really special, Shizuku.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.33,0:11:21.32,Tonari-internal/narrator,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,What was that look about?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.97,0:11:24.87,Tonari-main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,Have you ever felt empty inside?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.87,0:11:25.66,Tonari-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.41,0:11:27.46,Tonari-main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,So empty...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.91,0:11:29.00,Tonari-main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,you can't feel a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.06,0:11:31.46,Tonari-main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,Surrounded by darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.45,0:11:35.22,Tonari-main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,It really scares me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.94,0:11:42.81,Tonari-main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm not scared anymore...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.06,0:11:46.72,Tonari-main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,because I have you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.41,0:11:50.50,Tonari-internal/narrator,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,As Haru spoke,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.59,0:11:54.90,Tonari-internal/narrator,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,it almost seemed that he \Ncouldn't see anything at all,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.17,0:11:58.15,Tonari-internal/narrator,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,even though I was right there...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.15,0:12:00.27,Tonari-main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,Listen up.  Black holes are...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.27,0:12:01.40,Tonari-main,Natsu,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.83,0:12:02.91,Tonari-main,Natsu,0000,0000,0000,,Please help me study.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.95,0:12:24.05,Tonari-internal/narrator,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,There's definitely \Nsomething wrong with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.62,0:12:28.30,Tonari-internal/narrator,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,I never would have thought \Nabout these things before.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.07,0:12:32.49,Tonari-internal/narrator,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't care what other \Npeople thought about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.33,0:12:37.24,Tonari-internal/narrator,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,I need to study.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.24,0:12:39.05,Tonari-internal/narrator,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,Final exams are coming up.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.39,0:12:44.25,Tonari-internal/narrator,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,Tests, tests, tests...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.72,0:12:48.82,Tonari-internal/narrator,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,There's so much background noise \Nthat I can't concentrate.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.24,0:12:52.00,Tonari-main,Yana,0000,0000,0000,,Man, it's hot...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.00,0:12:54.08,Tonari-main,Seta,0000,0000,0000,,The upperclassmen aren't being fair.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.08,0:12:54.96,Tonari-main,Yana,0000,0000,0000,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.66,0:13:02.78,Tonari-main,Sasa,0000,0000,0000,,Mizutani-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.63,0:13:08.47,Tonari-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.47,0:13:09.65,Tonari-main,Sasa,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.65,0:13:12.08,Tonari-main,Sasa,0000,0000,0000,,You should try to remember the \Nfaces of your classmates.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.62,0:13:14.03,Tonari-main,Sasa,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Sasahara.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.03,0:13:15.35,Tonari-main,Sasa,0000,0000,0000,,You can call me Sasayan.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.91,0:13:16.98,Tonari-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.98,0:13:18.48,Tonari-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,So, did you need something?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.90,0:13:21.14,Tonari-main,Sasa,0000,0000,0000,,Not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.14,0:13:23.03,Tonari-main,Sasa,0000,0000,0000,,I'm interested in you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.07,0:13:24.97,Tonari-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.97,0:13:25.74,Tonari-main,Sasa,0000,0000,0000,,Because I like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.00,0:13:31.24,Tonari-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,You're lying.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.98,0:13:34.00,Tonari-main,Sasa,0000,0000,0000,,You can tell?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.23,0:13:37.34,Tonari-main,Sasa,0000,0000,0000,,You've been hanging out with Yoshida,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.34,0:13:38.94,Tonari-main,,0000,0000,0000,,so I was wondering what you were like.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.51,0:13:42.96,Tonari-main,Sasa,0000,0000,0000,,So, how did you get that \Ntruant to come to school?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.49,0:13:44.43,Tonari-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,Beats me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.43,0:13:47.14,Tonari-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,I have no idea what he's thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.85,0:13:51.44,Tonari-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm guessing he just wanted a \Nfriend.  Didn't matter who.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.40,0:13:55.37,Tonari-main,Sasa,0000,0000,0000,,I went to the same middle \Nschool as Yoshida.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.10,0:13:56.83,Tonari-main,Sasa,0000,0000,0000,,Did you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.39,0:14:00.88,Tonari-main,Sasa,0000,0000,0000,,He basically went three years \Nwithout coming to class.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.68,0:14:02.47,Tonari-internal/narrator,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.61,0:14:07.32,Tonari-internal/narrator,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,Well, anything's possible with Haru...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.37,0:14:09.57,Tonari-main,Sasa,0000,0000,0000,,My point is,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.31,0:14:13.40,Tonari-main,Sasa,0000,0000,0000,,the "who" must have mattered.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.39,0:14:21.07,Tonari-main,Seta,0000,0000,0000,,Sasayan, we're heading back!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.40,0:14:22.59,Tonari-main,Sasa,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.59,0:14:24.24,Tonari-main,Sasa,0000,0000,0000,,See ya, Mizutani-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.32,0:14:27.53,Tonari-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,Sasayan-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.54,0:14:30.51,Tonari-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,I have a favor to ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.47,0:14:44.14,Tonari-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.14,0:14:46.39,Tonari-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing, Natsume-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.39,0:14:48.09,Tonari-main,Natsu,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't mind me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.09,0:14:50.41,Tonari-main,Natsu,0000,0000,0000,,I'm in despair right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.76,0:14:53.08,Tonari-main,Sae,0000,0000,0000,,Yoshida-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.08,0:14:54.10,Tonari-main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.10,0:14:56.42,Tonari-main,Sae,0000,0000,0000,,You're not supposed to \Nbring roosters to school!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.42,0:14:58.04,Tonari-main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,You're such a pain!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.04,0:14:59.32,Tonari-main,Sae,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it right there, Yoshida-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.32,0:15:01.13,Tonari-main,Natsu,0000,0000,0000,,It's all over...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.13,0:15:03.85,Tonari-main,Natsu,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't understand anything \Nthat he taught me,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.85,0:15:05.76,Tonari-main,Natsu,0000,0000,0000,,and there's no time left...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.06,0:15:10.05,Tonari-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,Well, students are supposed to \Nspend their time studying.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.41,0:15:13.14,Tonari-main,Natsu,0000,0000,0000,,Hmph!  Who cares about school?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.14,0:15:15.51,Tonari-main,Natsu,0000,0000,0000,,The real me lives on the Internet!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.42,0:15:22.47,Tonari-main,Natsu,0000,0000,0000,,On the Internet,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.47,0:15:24.80,Tonari-main,Natsu,0000,0000,0000,,I'm constantly surrounded by friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.80,0:15:26.72,Tonari-main,Natsu,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone comes to me for help.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.53,0:15:31.65,Tonari-main,Natsu,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just an ordinary girl \Nwith hair problems.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.70,0:15:33.91,Tonari-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,Wouldn't that be considered
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.91,0:15:35.78,Tonari-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,living a lie?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.78,0:15:37.24,Tonari-main,Natsu,0000,0000,0000,,Just leave me alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.74,0:15:45.16,Tonari-main,Natsu,0000,0000,0000,,Someone who's smart and unfeeling \Nwould never understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.16,0:15:46.75,Tonari-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm not...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.61,0:15:50.20,Tonari-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care if I'm living a lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.94,0:15:54.03,Tonari-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,I want to be close to other people.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.43,0:15:59.52,Tonari-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,It's lonely when everyone \Nkeeps their distance.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.78,0:16:11.98,Tonari-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,Here, here, and here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.47,0:16:14.77,Tonari-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,If you focus on these \Nsections, you should pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.78,0:16:18.35,Tonari-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,There's a certain pattern \Nto the test questions used,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.84,0:16:21.21,Tonari-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,so if you nail these key \Npoints, you won't fail.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.07,0:16:23.42,Tonari-main,Natsu,0000,0000,0000,,H-Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.42,0:16:25.44,Tonari-main,Natsu,0000,0000,0000,,Mi-Mizutani-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.44,0:16:27.73,Tonari-internal/narrator,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,I still don't know what \Nthey're thinking,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.93,0:16:32.79,Tonari-internal/narrator,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,but I think I can understand \Nhow they feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.68,0:16:37.51,Tonari-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,Haru.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.99,0:16:39.93,Tonari-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want to go to \Nthe offline gathering?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.87,0:16:41.93,Tonari-main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,Yep!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.31,0:16:48.11,Tonari-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,Well, he's set on going,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.97,0:16:50.61,Tonari-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,so you need to pass the make-ups.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.61,0:16:53.06,Tonari-main,Natsu,0000,0000,0000,,M-Mitty!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.57,0:16:55.60,Tonari-main,Natsu,0000,0000,0000,,The make-ups are tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.60,0:16:57.37,Tonari-main,Natsu,0000,0000,0000,,Is that enough time?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.40,0:17:02.00,Tonari-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.71,0:17:06.29,Tonari-main,Natsu,0000,0000,0000,,No turning back now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.74,0:17:10.25,Tonari-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,Stop sleeping!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.25,0:17:13.27,Tonari-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,Why can't you memorize \Na simple formula?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.27,0:17:13.96,Tonari-main,Natsu,0000,0000,0000,,Evil!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.96,0:17:17.03,Tonari-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,You realize I'm pulling \Nan all-nighter for you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.03,0:17:19.51,Tonari-main,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you kids studying here?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.51,0:17:21.60,Tonari-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,Stop sleeping!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.14,0:17:24.48,Tonari-main,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,Can I go home yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.03,0:17:30.19,Tonari-internal/narrator,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to my hard work,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.66,0:17:33.68,Tonari-internal/narrator,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,Natsume-san was exonerated \Nfrom the remedial class.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.68,0:17:36.20,Tonari-main,Natsu,0000,0000,0000,,My highest score ever!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.20,0:17:37.84,Tonari-internal/narrator,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,But on Monday...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.91,0:17:42.70,Tonari-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,Haru-kun ruined everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.70,0:17:44.79,Tonari-main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,I'm never going to one of those again.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.90,0:17:49.98,Tonari-main,Natsu,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't get a chance \Nto talk to any girls...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.33,0:17:55.43,Tonari-main,Natsu,0000,0000,0000,,Then, Haru-kun got in a fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.21,0:17:55.43,Tonari-flashbackinternal,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,Moron!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.43,0:17:57.41,Tonari-flashbackinternal,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,The Qilin is an OOPArt!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.82,0:18:04.06,Chalkboard-small,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}Science\NClassical Literature\NMusic\NWorld History\NEnglish\Home Economics
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.35,0:18:01.85,Tonari-main,Natsu,0000,0000,0000,,When I logged on to the community again,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.85,0:18:04.06,Tonari-main,Natsu,0000,0000,0000,,everybody gave me the cold shoulder.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.06,0:18:06.77,hscommunity2,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,High School Community
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.28,0:18:06.77,Tonari-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,Told you so.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.77,0:18:07.97,Tonari-main,Natsu,0000,0000,0000,,I quit.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.76,0:18:12.68,Tonari-main,Sae,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.68,0:18:14.18,Tonari-main,Sae,0000,0000,0000,,Yoshida-kun!  Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.18,0:18:16.99,Tonari-main,Sae,0000,0000,0000,,How many times must I tell you \Nnot to bring this rooster?!  Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.39,0:18:18.11,Tonari-main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.55,0:18:20.00,Tonari-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,I forgot to tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.00,0:18:20.74,Tonari-main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.55,0:18:26.31,Tonari-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,Sasahara-kun volunteered to \Ntake care of the rooster.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.31,0:18:28.87,Tonari-main,Sasa,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, I like fried chicken.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.73,0:18:32.13,Tonari-main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.65,0:18:35.30,Tonari-main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Shizuku?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.01,0:18:39.64,Tonari-main,Natsu,0000,0000,0000,,Mitty, Haru-kun's looking for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.17,0:18:42.64,Tonari-main,Natsu,0000,0000,0000,,He reminds me of when my \Ndad's looking for his socks.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.09,0:18:44.73,Tonari-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.73,0:18:46.99,Tonari-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,If he finds me, it'll get noisy again.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.52,0:18:50.15,Tonari-main,Natsu,0000,0000,0000,,You look tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.58,0:18:51.42,Tonari-main,Natsu,0000,0000,0000,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.42,0:18:53.75,Tonari-main,Natsu,0000,0000,0000,,I'll buy you something to drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.75,0:18:55.26,Tonari-main,Natsu,0000,0000,0000,,To thank you for helping me study.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.69,0:19:02.88,Tonari-internal/narrator,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,Finally, some peace and quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.60,0:19:06.07,Tonari-internal/narrator,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,I've been spending more time
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.07,0:19:08.37,Tonari-internal/narrator,,0000,0000,0000,,around other people than \NI thought was possible,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.02,0:19:11.38,Tonari-internal/narrator,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,so I'm exhausted.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.09,0:19:24.89,Tonari-main,Natsu,0000,0000,0000,,Mitty, I bought you some juice...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.88,0:19:33.56,Tonari-main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,Shh.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.94,0:19:43.12,Tonari-internal/narrator,Natsu,0000,0000,0000,,I'm cheering for you, Haru-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.79,0:20:03.41,Tonari-main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,Yo.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.85,0:20:05.26,Tonari-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,Ha-Haru?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.26,0:20:06.64,Tonari-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,When did you...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.35,0:20:08.93,Tonari-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I'm missing class!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.54,0:20:16.27,Tonari-main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,Go back to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.76,0:20:20.61,Tonari-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn't you wake me up?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.61,0:20:21.52,Tonari-main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.52,0:20:23.03,Tonari-main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,You were out like a light.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.48,0:20:24.66,Tonari-main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,I thought it was cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.13,0:20:27.60,Tonari-internal/narrator,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.44,0:20:31.42,Tonari-internal/narrator,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,I have to wonder if he's \Ndoing this on purpose.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.34,0:20:40.00,Tonari-internal/narrator,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,This is the first time \NI've ever skipped class.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.15,0:20:46.57,Tonari-internal/narrator,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,It's a beautiful day.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.41,0:20:51.24,Tonari-internal/narrator,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,The old me
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.90,0:20:55.08,Tonari-internal/narrator,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,would never have known how \Nblue the afternoon sky
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.08,0:20:56.95,Tonari-internal/narrator,,0000,0000,0000,,looks from the roof.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.59,0:21:03.54,Tonari-internal/narrator,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,My world is growing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.15,0:21:09.84,Tonari-internal/narrator,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,What I once considered background noise
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.06,0:21:12.84,Tonari-internal/narrator,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,is now comforting.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.06,0:21:20.53,Tonari-internal/narrator,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,It feels so good.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.55,0:21:23.43,Tonari-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,Haru.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.43,0:21:24.33,Tonari-main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.29,0:21:29.76,Tonari-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad we met.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.93,0:21:34.49,Tonari-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,Before, I only cared about studying,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.04,0:21:37.24,Tonari-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,but I'm going to start enjoying myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.00,0:21:41.40,Tonari-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,I love you, Haru.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.19,0:21:44.73,Tonari-internal/narrator,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,My values are changing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.39,0:21:49.32,Tonari-internal/narrator,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps, my world has also changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.01,0:21:51.99,Tonari-internal/narrator,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,If so,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.91,0:21:54.87,Tonari-internal/narrator,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,my world was changed
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.33,0:21:56.44,Tonari-internal/narrator,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,by Haru.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.15,0:23:35.35,Tonari-main,Sae,0000,0000,0000,,Natsume-san, do you have a moment?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.35,0:23:36.47,Tonari-main,Natsu,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.44,0:23:48.44,asako,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,Helpful Advice from Golubaeser Asako
