Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.36,0:23:53.37,computer text,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,into a human shape
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.12,0:23:57.12,computer text,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}and your own hair
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.83,0:23:59.83,computer text2,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,burn
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.54,0:24:03.25,computer text3,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,First, secure two strands of hair from the target\Nto make him or her yours
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.83,0:24:08.15,Tonari-main,Natsu,0000,0000,0000,,How did you get here?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.49,0:24:09.71,Tonari-main,Natsu,0000,0000,0000,,Are you lost?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.29,0:24:13.30,Tonari-main,Natsu,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, have you heard this song before?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.30,0:24:15.47,Tonari-main,Natsu,0000,0000,0000,,Chicken, chicken, chicken!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.47,0:24:17.54,Tonari-main,Natsu,0000,0000,0000,,Chicken, chicken!
