Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.01,0:24:21.02,Tonari-Next-ep-title,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,Nuisance
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.54,0:24:20.54,Tonari-main,Natsu,0000,0000,0000,,Time to chow down!
